It's a Raseirian Guard.	這是一名拉希爾衛兵。
This man must be the boss.	這個人一定是頭目。
Ugarte is being dragged off to the dungeon.	烏加特被拖去地牢了。
gard&Ugarte	衛兵&烏加特
the barricade	路障
The alley is securely blocked by a barricade of boards.  You can barely discern a sign reading: "This street closed by order of Khaveen!"	巷子被木製路障牢牢擋住。你勉強能看清一塊寫著:「此街奉哈維因之命封閉!」的告示。
The alley is securely blocked by a barricade of boards.  You can barely discern a sign reading: "The smuggling of water is a capital crime!"	巷子被木製路障牢牢擋住。你勉強能看清一塊寫著:「走私水是死罪!」的告示。
the cracked and dirty	龜裂又骯髒的
The mosaic is cracked and dirty.	這幅鑲嵌畫龜裂又骯髒。
Once, this window overlooked a clean and busy Plaza.	這扇窗戶曾經俯瞰著一座乾淨又繁忙的廣場。
No one has looked out of this window onto the Plaza for a long, long time.	已經很久很久沒有人從這扇窗戶望向廣場了。
the magical light	魔法光芒
The alley is securely blocked by a barricade of boards.  You can barely discern a sign reading: "All Fed-Ex packages must be out by 2:30!"	巷子被木製路障牢牢擋住。你勉強能看清一塊寫著:「所有 Fed-Ex 包裹必須在 2:30 前送出!」的告示。
You see a dark foreboding passage leading North.  The street sign reads: "Any order from a guard is a rule!"	你看見一條陰森可怖的通道向北延伸。街道告示寫著:「衛兵的命令就是規矩!」
the alley leading East	通往東邊的巷子
You see a dark foreboding passage leading East.  The street sign reads: "Everything not mandatory is forbidden!"	你看見一條陰森可怖的通道向東延伸。街道告示寫著:「凡非強制之事皆被禁止!」
the balcony	陽台
the door to the guards' quarters	衛兵宿舍的門
the curtain	窗簾
the curtains	窗簾
