the ghost	幽靈
the ritual candle	儀式蠟燭
The candles are a crucial part of the Iblis ritual.	這些蠟燭是伊布利斯儀式中不可或缺的一部分。
the statue of Iblis	伊布利斯的雕像
It's the statue that has held Iblis for a Thousand Years and a Year.	這座雕像已封印伊布利斯一千零一年。
Shake, Rattle and Roll!	天搖地動,滾滾而去!
the magic rope	魔法繩索
Nice of you to drop in!	你能「掉」下來真好啊!
Bye, rope	再見了,繩索
Brainless and Painless	沒有腦子,毫無痛楚
a candle	一根蠟燭
The candles are positioned at the six apexes of the hexagram.	蠟燭被放置在六芒星的六個頂點上。
The Calm spell must have worn off of Khaveen.  He seems confused, but very angry.	鎮靜咒一定已經在哈維因身上失效了。他看起來很困惑,但非常憤怒。
Rocky	洛基
the djinni	精靈
the moon	月亮
