the red glow	紅色光芒
There is a red glow in another chamber beyond this one.	這個房間之外的另一個房間中,透出紅色的光芒。
Wrong!	錯了!
the ancient doors	古老的門
the reflection of your lamp.	你油燈的倒影。
the stalactite	鐘乳石
Part of the stalactite that fell on you.	掉落在你身上的鐘乳石碎片。
Its your lamp that you've been carrying around.	這是你一直隨身攜帶的油燈。
Bye bye!!	再見了!!
the jewels and gold	珠寶與黃金
