A Zap for a Permanent Nap	一道電擊,長眠不起
the boulder	巨石
Large boulders surround the door.	巨石環繞著這扇門。
Man who go about in desert sun soon find himself Medium well	男人若在沙漠烈日下遊蕩,不久便會發現自己被烤到五分熟
He who turns to run away sometimes find knife in back	轉身逃跑之人,有時會發現背後插著一把刀
Freedom is like temper	自由就像脾氣
If fire burns too bright, put damper on lamp	若火燒得太旺,便替油燈裝上調節閥
Your saurus is like reflection in pool	你的索魯斯,如同水池中的倒影
